00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:59.000
I recommend you to change the guitar strings one or two days before your gig.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Because it can happen too many things...

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:08.000
If your strings have months.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:15.000
and I know people that have years with the same strings.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:19.000
