00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.000
It happened several times.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Then I learned that I have to play always with New Strings.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:42.000
Obviously, if you play often with your band. One or two times a weekend or more...

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:49.000
It wouldn't be required you to replace your strings every time you play, because your strings will last some time.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:53.000
But if you play one or two times a month

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:59.000
change your strings often so you are ensured.

