Sound checking is very important.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:33.000
And the more important thing is that you make sure that you have good sound return.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:37.000
Good sound return, not only of your instrument...

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:41.000
that is very important, because you have difficulties to hear your instrument...

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:44.000
...you would have to play from memory...

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:47.000
...and you wouldn't be comfortable.

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:53.000
And it's also important to have good sound return from your band mates instruments

00:03:53.000 --> 00:04:00.000
Because you could get lost and it could be difficult to play songs correctly.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:03.000
So, it's very important when you play live.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:12.000
And now, this is the most important Tip, I think...

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:15.000
Too many people get nervous when playing live

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:22.000
So, it's very important to relax

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:29.000
There are too many techniques to avoid get nervous when you get on the stage...

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:36.000
But the more important is that you relax and think as if you are playing in a rehearsal.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:41.000
That's very important.

